{
  "stem": "26576.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And those are-- this is something that I really will never forget, because what did happen the day the war broke out, my father said to-- to my mother and actual to me that he is going to walk over-- he is going to walk, and he wants us to pack a few things and to go in a different direction.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said he is going because there were talks already about-- that he always had in mind to walk over to the Russian side, to-- to the Russians, because he felt that this-- this way maybe he'll survive.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember we packed a few things on a little-- I even don't know what you call it-- on a little-- so like it was-- it was a carriage, not a horse an carriage, but just-- and we walked.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we walked maybe 50 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, my mother wasn't a great walker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were three little kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was sort like the main star there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was pushing the thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly, in the middle of nowhere, we were 70 kilometers out of Sosnowiec, we were surrounded by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in a very-- you know, it was a field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw the Germans coming with those big bayonets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And halt, halt!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it's something for many, many years, if I was dreaming about something terrible, this was that feeling of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "German uniform, it was German, and surrounding us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't hit us or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They just said back, back, zuruck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was-- we came back to Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Must have been the third day of the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My father wasn't home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A few days later, he also turned up.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
